Description








                        
	
	
    
    
	
			There's so much to love about this Judith Ripka sterling silver bracelet. From the berge-motif panther links to the heart stations that shine with round cubic zirconia Diamonique(R) simulated diamonds, the bracelet is sure to become an instant favorite. From Judith Ripka.
	    
  Sterling silverTotal Diamonique simulated diamond weight is approximately 1.65 carats; simulated diamonds are cubic zirconiaBerge-motif panther links; heart stations and prong-set, round Diamonique simulated diamondsHidden box clasp with safety barDue to the design elements of this bracelet, the fit and length measurements may differ; please order according to fit8" Fit: measures approximately 7-3/4"L x 3/8"WImported 




