Description








                        
	
	
    
    
	
			Unlock the look of love. Judith Ripka presents this dazzling sterling silver heart and key charm bracelet--boasting a Diamonique(R) simulated diamond heart and key charm dangling near a textured lobster claw clasp with additional Diamonique simulated diamonds. From Judith Ripka.Sterling Silver, Black Rhodium-Plated Sterling Silver, or Chocolate Color-Plated Sterling Silver.For more details on this bracelet's fit, please refer to Wrist Assist--the Bracelet Fit Guide above.
	    
  Sterling silverTotal Diamonique simulated diamond weight is approximately 8/10 caratPave-set Diamonique  simulated diamond heart and key charm near claspTextured heart-design lobster claw clasp with Diamonique simulated diamondsDue to the design elements of this bracelet, the fit and length measurements may differ; please order according to fit8" Fit: measures approximately 8-1/4"L x 3/8"WCharm measures approximately 3/4"L x 3/4"WMade in Italy 




